io.gearpump.cluster.client

Class ClientContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.gearpump.cluster.client.ClientContext
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EmbeddedRuntimeEnvironment.EmbeddedClientContext, RuntimeEnvironment.RemoteClientContext

    public class ClientContext
extends java.lang.Object
    ClientContext is a user facing utility to interact with the master. (e.g. submit/manage an application).
